# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Todoist API — Required for dynacat-todoist widgets
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Add these variables to the .env file used by your Dynacat instance.
# They are referenced in widget config as ${TODOIST_API_TOKEN}, etc.
#
# How to find your Todoist API token:
#   1. Log in to Todoist
#   2. Go to Settings → Integrations → Developer
#   3. Copy the API token shown under "API token"
#   Docs: https://todoist.com/help/articles/find-your-api-token-Jpzx9IIlB
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# REQUIRED — Your personal Todoist API token
TODOIST_API_TOKEN=your_personal_api_token_here
